Version history for jquery-hover-dropdown-box
https://github.com/mugifly/jquery-hover-dropdown-box/

1.3.0  2014-xx-xx
   - [Add] onClose function option when using hover model (Thanks: needwrong).
   - [Add] width and height option (Thanks: needwrong).

1.2.0  2013-09-06 (alpha)
   - [Add] 'onChange' event.
   - [Add] 'onInputText' event (It are different to parameters from 'onTextInput' event).
   - [Fix] Some fixes of a code and a document.
   - [Change] The 'onTextinput' event is deprecated.
   - [Change] Renamed the 'getInputObject' method of the item object => 'inputElement'.
     ('getInputObject' method is deprecated.)

1.1.0  2013-09-06 (alpha)
   - [Fix] Separate the parent dom and the trigger dom, on Hover mode.
   - [Fix] Support for stylesheet in various existing environment.
   - [Fix] Malfuction about the default value of a checkbox
   - [Change] Renamed the 'inputSelected' option of an items => 'inputChecked'
     ('inputSelected' option is deprecated.)

1.0.0  2013-08-23 (alpha)
   - Initial release (alpha)
